---
title: "transmit (Payment Abstraction V2 - PriceManager)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_access: onlyRole(PRICE_ADMIN_ROLE)
    q_check_access --> q_check_empty: check unverifiedReports.length
    q_check_empty --> q_revert_empty: length == 0
    q_revert_empty --> [*]: revert EmptyList()
    q_check_empty --> q_pre_validate: length > 0

    q_pre_validate --> q_iter_pre: for report in unverifiedReports
    q_iter_pre --> q_decode_feed_id: decode reportData, extract dataStreamsFeedId
    q_decode_feed_id --> q_check_allowlist: check s_dataStreamsFeedIdToAsset
    q_check_allowlist --> q_revert_not_allowed: asset == address(0)
    q_revert_not_allowed --> [*]: revert FeedNotAllowlisted()
    q_check_allowlist --> q_iter_pre: feed is allowlisted
    q_iter_pre --> q_verify_bulk: pre-validation complete

    q_verify_bulk --> q_iter_verified: verifiedReports = verifierProxy.verifyBulk(reports)

    q_iter_verified --> q_decode_report: for report in verifiedReports
    q_decode_report --> q_get_asset: report = abi.decode(ReportV3)
    q_get_asset --> q_check_stale: asset = s_dataStreamsFeedIdToAsset[feedId]
    q_check_stale --> q_revert_stale: observationsTimestamp < block.timestamp - stalenessThreshold
    q_revert_stale --> [*]: revert StaleFeedData()
    q_check_stale --> q_scale_price: price not stale

    q_scale_price --> q_check_zero: scale usdPrice to 18 decimals
    q_check_zero --> q_revert_zero: usdPrice == 0
    q_revert_zero --> [*]: revert ZeroFeedData()
    q_check_zero --> q_store: usdPrice > 0

    q_store --> q_iter_verified: s_dataStreamsPrice[asset] = DataStreamsPriceInfo(usdPrice, timestamp)
    q_iter_verified --> [*]: all reports processed

    note right of q_verify_bulk
        INV-001: Reports are verified through external VerifierProxy before storage
        INV-002: Only allowlisted feed IDs are accepted
        INV-003: Prices are scaled to 18 decimals uniformly
        INV-004: Stale and zero prices are rejected
        INV-005: Pre-validation loop checks allowlisting BEFORE bulk verification (gas optimization)
    end note
